        <p class="text-muted">Â© 2019 Jason Mayfield. Thank You to Etiene Dalcol. Powered by <a href="http://sailorproject.org" target="_blank">Sailor MVC</a>
        - <a href="http://lua.org" target="_blank">Lua</a> -
         Icon from  <a href="https://pngtree.com/">pngtree.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>


